Title: IPMI Management Board: Fix "Discovery Session no longer connected"
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0p19
Date: 1602769303
Class: fix

Fix unstable IPMI management board monitoring: Once an IPMI management board
was configured, the Check_MK or Check_MK Discovery service could show
{{Discovery Session no longer connected}} after trying to contact the host
multiple times.
